main event: Observers in Kansas City reported seeing unidentified lights in the sky that displayed darting movements before disappearing.
interesting points: The observers could not obtain a clear view of the objects due to poor visibility conditions., They estimated that the lights appeared to be aircraft reflecting city lights., The objects displayed fuzzy and blurred edges., Observers estimated the speed of the objects to be around 400-500 mph., The sighting duration was approximately 3 minutes.
witness description: female, age 37, located inside a building during the observation
